name: Eat The Bankers (2021) - David W. J. Lloyd
description: Size 1600px x 680px animated GIF. Single Edition 1 of 1. Reveal the horror hidden in a $100 bill! Originally made by myself to be a part of the ill-fated Not Art Club piece The Last Bell, this is the full version which was designed to match a 100th section of a $100 bill, animated to blend with the section of the $100 bill that inspired the art. Originally made from mixed media on paper, then scanned with added digital elements. Twitter: @daytripart Insta: @d.w.j.lloyd - Copyright 2021 - David W. J. Lloyd.
